1
00:00:01,146 --> 00:00:08,482
I live in a very old town which is surrounded by beautiful woods.
我住在一个古老小镇上, 被美丽的树林环绕着.

2
00:00:08,845 --> 00:00:11,903
It is a famous beauty spot.
这是一个著名的风景胜地.

3
00:00:12,481 --> 00:00:19,189
On Sundays, hundreds of people come from the city to see our town 
每适星期天,有成百的人从城里来观赏我们的小镇,

4
00:00:19,326 --> 00:00:22,081
and to walk through the woods.
并在树林中散步.

5
00:00:23,437 --> 00:00:29,824
Visitors have been asked to keep the woods clean and tidy.
游客已被告知要保持树林的整洁.

6
00:00:30,214 --> 00:00:34,402
Litter baskets have been placed under the trees,
树下都已设置了废物筐,

7
00:00:34,923 --> 00:00:39,347
but people still throw their rubbish everywhere.
但是人们仍到处扔垃圾.

8
00:00:40,099 --> 00:00:45,712
Last Wednesday, I went for a walk in the woods.
上星期三我到树林里去散步.

9
00:00:46,469 --> 00:00:50,714
What I saw made me very sad.
我所见到的一切使我非常难过.

10
00:00:51,615 --> 00:00:58,627
I counted seven old cars and three old refrigerators.
我数了一下,有7辆旧汽车和3个旧冰箱.

11
00:00:59,017 --> 00:01:01,964
The litter baskets were empty
废物筐是空的,

12
00:01:02,290 --> 00:01:10,712
and the ground was covered with pieces of paper, cigarette ends, old tyres, 
而满地都是纸片、烟头、旧轮胎,

13
00:01:11,476 --> 00:01:15,241
empty bottles and rusty tins.
空瓶子和生锈的空罐头盒.

14
00:01:15,973 --> 00:01:20,483
Among the rubbish, I found a sign which said,
在垃圾中我发现了一块牌子,上面写着：

15
00:01:21,415 --> 00:01:27,891
Anyone who leaves litter in these woods will be prosecuted!'
“凡在此树林里丢弃垃圾者,将依法处置.”

